  26 May 2012; Tomáš Chvátal <scarabeus@gentoo.org> gpscorrelate-1.6.1.ebuild:
  Depend also on xml-dtd. Fixes bug#384133.

  24 May 2012; Tomáš Chvátal <scarabeus@gentoo.org> gpscorrelate-1.6.1.ebuild:
  Add missing dependency over pkgconfig.

  09 Jun 2011; Tomáš Chvátal <scarabeus@gentoo.org>
  files/gpscorrelate-1.6.1-makefile.patch:
  Do not allow pollution of CLIBS variable. Fixes bug #370463.

  08 Jun 2011; Tomáš Chvátal <scarabeus@gentoo.org>
  gpscorrelate-1.6.1.ebuild, files/gpscorrelate-1.6.1-makefile.patch:
  Update the makefile patch so the gtk is really optional.

*gpscorrelate-1.6.1 (07 Jun 2011)

  07 Jun 2011; Tomáš Chvátal <scarabeus@gentoo.org>
  -gpscorrelate-1.5.6.ebuild, -files/gpscorrelate-1.5.6-cflags.patch,
